---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Base from '../base.css';
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Astro.">
    <main>
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 2xl:grid-cols-5">
            <div class="
            2xl:col-span-2
            px-8 py-12 lg:px-12 lg:py-24
         max-w-md sm:max-w-xl lg:max-w-full
         mx-auto xl:mr-0">
                <div class="xl:max-w-xl">
                    <img class="h-10" src="/assets/logo.svg" alt="Workcation">
                    <img class="lg:hidden mt-6 sm:mt-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl sm:h-64 sm:w-full object-cover object-center"
                         src="/assets/beach-work.jpeg" alt="Woman workcationing on the beach">
                    <h1 class="mt-6 sm:mt-8 text-2xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800">
                        You can work from anywhere.
                        <br>
                        <span class="text-indigo-500">Take advantage of it.</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="mt-6 sm:mt-8 text-gray-600 sm:text-xl">
                        Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of
                        classical
                        Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin
                        professor at
                        Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur,
                        from
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-4 sm:mt-6">
                        <a href="#" class="btn">Book
                            your escape</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden lg:block relative 2xl:col-span-3">
                <img class="absolute inset-0 w-full max-w-6xl h-full object-cover object-center"
                     src="/assets/beach-work.jpeg"
                     alt="Woman workcationing on the beach">
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
